Child Safety Policy

1. Commitment to Child Safety
   Murmur is committed to maintaining a safe and respectful environment. We strictly prohibit any content involving child exploitation, abuse, or endangerment.

2. Reporting Mechanism
   Users can report inappropriate content directly within the app or by contacting contact@ngksolutions.com.

3. Content Moderation
   Our team actively reviews reported content and takes immediate action against violations.

4. Legal Compliance
   Murmur complies with all applicable child protection laws and guidelines.

5. Contact for Child Safety
   For any concerns regarding child safety, please reach out to contact@ngksolutions.com.
